  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients who have provided written informed consent

          -  Patients over 18 years old

          -  Patients less than 70 years old

          -  Patient presenting with a fracture of the trochanter (type 1 to 6 according to the
             Ender classification, and A1 and A2 according tyo the AO classification (Association
             suisse pour l'étude de l'Ostéosynthèse : classification internationale)

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Adult under guardianship

          -  Patients not covered by national health insurance

          -  Pregnant or breast-feeding women

          -  Unable to walk independently before the trauma

          -  Patients with dementia
      </textblock>
